snippet.title: Renowned Explorers: More To Explore, Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/460390/
GOG: https://www.gog.com/game/renowned_explorers_more_to_explore

Renowned Explorers: More To Explore is a paid expansion pack for Renowned Explorers that further increases the replay value of the original game by offering new expeditions, more strategic variety, crew relationships and character backstories
